<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:13:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>提案作者表示，全球2%的财富税是对超级富豪征税的起点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-2-wealth-levy-starting-point-taxing-super-rich-says-proposal-author-2024-06-25/</link><description>法国经济学家加布里埃尔·祖克曼 (Gabriel Zucman) 周二表示，对超过 10 亿美元的财富每年征收 2% 的税，是增加征税不足的亿万富翁负担的全球提案的起点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-2-wealth-levy-starting-point-taxing-super-rich-says-proposal-author-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>国际特赦组织表示，Shein 的潜在 IPO 将成为伦敦证券交易所的“耻辱徽章”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sheins-potential-ipo-be-badge-shame-lse-amnesty-international-says-2024-06-25/</link><description>英国国际特赦组织周二表示，Shein 潜在的伦敦首次公开募股将给伦敦证券交易所带来“耻辱”，因为这家快时尚公司的劳工和人权标准“值得怀疑”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sheins-potential-ipo-be-badge-shame-lse-amnesty-international-says-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔哈撒韦加速中国比亚迪的销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/berkshire-hathaway-accelerates-sales-chinas-byd-2024-06-25/</link><description>沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司加速出售中国最大电动汽车销售商比亚迪的股份。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:34:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/berkshire-hathaway-accelerates-sales-chinas-byd-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>副部长表示，中国欢迎美国乳制品企业在华扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-welcomes-us-dairy-firms-expanding-country-vice-minister-says-2024-06-25/</link><description>商务部副部长王受文周二表示，中国欢迎包括美国在内的各国乳制品企业扩大在中国市场的业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 12:12:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-welcomes-us-dairy-firms-expanding-country-vice-minister-says-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>致命的电池厂火灾凸显了韩国农民工面临的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/deadly-battery-plant-fire-highlights-risks-south-koreas-migrant-workers-2024-06-25/</link><description>周二，蔡成范 (Chae Sung-bum) 流着泪赶到韩国首都郊区的一家电池厂，希望能找到女儿的尸体，或者至少是能识别她身份的项链，此前该工厂发生致命火灾，导致女儿和其他 22 人死亡。工人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 10:37:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/deadly-battery-plant-fire-highlights-risks-south-koreas-migrant-workers-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>据日经新闻报道，日产将于年底开始为东风汽车生产电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-start-producing-evs-dongfeng-motor-by-year-end-nikkei-reports-2024-06-25/</link><description>据《日经新闻》周二报道，日产汽车将于年底前在其中国合资伙伴东风汽车的武汉工厂生产电动汽车，这是该汽车制造商中国业务面临压力的迹象。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 10:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-start-producing-evs-dongfeng-motor-by-year-end-nikkei-reports-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>警方称，中国拘留了持刀袭击日本校车的嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-detains-suspect-knife-attack-japanese-school-bus-police-say-2024-06-25/</link><description>地方当局周二表示，中国警方拘留了一名男子，该男子涉嫌持刀袭击东部城市苏州一所日本学校使用的公交车，造成三人受伤，其中包括两名日本公民。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:30:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-detains-suspect-knife-attack-japanese-school-bus-police-say-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>伦敦证券交易所数据显示，印度和中国是五月份俄罗斯燃料油的最大买家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/india-china-top-buyers-russian-fuel-oil-may-lseg-data-shows-2024-06-25/</link><description>交易商称，伦敦证券交易所数据显示，印度和中国是 5 月份俄罗斯海运燃料油和减压柴油 (VGO) 出口的最大目的地。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/india-china-top-buyers-russian-fuel-oil-may-lseg-data-shows-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>美元主导地位稳固，金砖国家在去美元化方面没有取得进展——报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/us-dollars-dominance-secure-brics-see-no-progress-de-dollarization-report-2024-06-25/</link><description>大西洋理事会地缘经济中心的一项新研究显示，美元仍然是世界主要储备货币，欧元和所谓的金砖国家都未能减少全球对美元的依赖。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/us-dollars-dominance-secure-brics-see-no-progress-de-dollarization-report-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>埃克森美孚领导的圭亚那石油集团 2023 年净值跃升，利润率超过英伟达</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-led-guyana-oil-groups-net-jumps-2023-margins-top-nvidias-2024-06-25/</link><description>政府数据显示，圭亚那去年与埃克森美孚领导的南美国家财团达成的利润丰厚的协议为合作伙伴带来了 63.3 亿美元的收入，净利润高于芯片制造商英伟达公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:05:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-led-guyana-oil-groups-net-jumps-2023-margins-top-nvidias-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促欧盟撤销对中国企业与俄罗斯联系的制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-urges-eu-revoke-sanctions-chinese-firms-over-russian-links-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国周二敦促欧盟撤销对其认为支持俄罗斯乌克兰战争的中国公司的制裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 08:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-urges-eu-revoke-sanctions-chinese-firms-over-russian-links-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>诺和诺德减肥药Wegovy在中国获批</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-says-semaglutide-approved-long-term-weight-management-china-2024-06-25/</link><description>诺和诺德公司周二表示，其广受欢迎的减肥药Wegovy已在中国获得批准，中国是世界第二大经济体，也是超重或肥胖人数最多的国家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:19:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-says-semaglutide-approved-long-term-weight-management-china-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国嫦娥六号月球探测器返回地球</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-change-6-moon-probe-lands-back-earth-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国嫦娥六号月球探测器周二在内蒙古北部地区着陆，使中国成为第一个从月球背面带回样本的国家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:19:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-change-6-moon-probe-lands-back-earth-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>47名香港民主党人的里程碑式审判进入宣判前的最后阶段</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/landmark-trial-47-hong-kong-democrats-enters-final-stretch-before-sentencing-2024-06-25/</link><description>香港有史以来规模最大的针对香港民主反对派的国家安全审判的减刑请求于周二启动，预计这是宣判前的最后阶段，部分被告可能被判处终身监禁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 04:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/landmark-trial-47-hong-kong-democrats-enters-final-stretch-before-sentencing-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国反击西方电动汽车、锂电池产能过剩指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-its-evs-lithium-batteries-meet-domestic-demand-enrich-global-supply-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国总理李强在大连举行的世界经济论坛会议上发表讲话，回击了美国和欧盟的指控，即中国企业从不公平补贴中受益，并准备用廉价的绿色技术涌入其市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 03:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-its-evs-lithium-batteries-meet-domestic-demand-enrich-global-supply-2024-06-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>